``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019%>% filter(Año == 2019)%>% rename(NUAL = 'NA') ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} head(Congreso_local_2019_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` # A tibble: 6 × 16 Año ID_ESTADO NOMBRE_ESTADO PAN PRI PRD PT PVEM MC MORENA NUAL 1 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 11630 1899 1429 1056 1049 7511 18212 0 2 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 16469 2178 1287 942 1016 5693 21407 0 3 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 22041 4183 1673 1125 1172 3446 23284 0 4 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 10782 2213 1002 1016 828 2330 18161 0 5 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 9281 2220 1019 1099 774 4481 17967 0 6 2019 2 BAJA CALIFOR… 9176 4823 2871 1329 2244 2576 17810 0 # ℹ 5 more variables: PES , Otro , CAND_IND1 , CAND_IND2 , # CAND_IND3 ``` ::: ::: ### Manipulación de Datos: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f%>% gather(key = Partido, value=Votos, PAN:CAND_IND3) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f[!is.na(Congreso_local_2019_f$Votos),] ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} reactable(Congreso_local_2019_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Agrupaciones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f%>% group_by(ID_ESTADO, NOMBRE_ESTADO, Partido)%>% reframe(Votos = sum(Votos))%>% arrange((ID_ESTADO)) reactable(Congreso_local_2019_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} suma_2020 <- Congreso_local_2019_f%>% group_by(ID_ESTADO, NOMBRE_ESTADO)%>% reframe(Votos1 = sum(Votos)) reactable(suma_2020) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Uniones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f %>% left_join(suma_2020, by = c("ID_ESTADO", "NOMBRE_ESTADO")) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f%>% mutate(Proporcion= (Votos/Votos1)*(100)) reactable(Congreso_local_2019_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: ### Manupulación de Datos: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integrantes2019 <- integrantes2019%>% gather(key = Sexo, value= Curules, Hombres:Mujeres) reactable(integrantes2019) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integrantes2019 <- integrantes2019%>% replace_na(list(Curules = 0)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integrantes2019 <- integrantes2019%>% filter(Curules != 0) ``` ::: ### Uniones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Congreso_local_2019_f <- Congreso_local_2019_f%>% inner_join(integrantes2019, by = c("ID_ESTADO", "Partido")) reactable(Congreso_local_2019_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
